<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Confirmation</title>
  <style>
      .container {
          margin-top: 20px;
          max-width: 600px;
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: auto;
          padding: 20px;
          border: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
          border-radius: 5px;
          background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .card {
          border: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
          border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .card-header {
          background-color: #007bff;
          color: #ffffff;
          padding: 10px;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
          border-top-left-radius: 5px;
          border-top-right-radius: 5px;
      }
      .card-body {
          padding: 20px;
      }
      .table {
          width: 100%;
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
          color: #212529;
          border-collapse: collapse;
      }
      .table th, .table td {
          padding: 0.75rem;
          vertical-align: top;
          border-top: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
      }
      .table thead th {
          vertical-align: bottom;
          border-bottom: 2px solid #e3e3e3;
      }
      .table tbody + tbody {
          border-top: 2px solid #e3e3e3;
      }
      .table-striped tbody tr:nth-of-type(odd) {
          background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <h3>Order Confirmation from The Pragmatic Store</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p>Dear <%= @order.name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for your recent purchase from The Pragmatic Store!</p>
      <p>We are pleased to confirm your order (ID: <%= @order.id %>) and provide the details of the items you have selected:</p>
      <table class="table table-striped">
        <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Qty</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        <%= render @order.line_items %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>We appreciate your business and are committed to providing you with the best service. You will receive a separate email with the tracking information once your order has shipped.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our customer service team at <a href="mailto:support@pragmaticstore.com">support@pragmaticstore.com</a>.</p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing The Pragmatic Store. We hope you enjoy your purchase!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Pragmatic Store Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>